Name: chronic canaliculitis
Definition: A lacrimal apparatus disease that is characterized by longstanding inflammation of the lacrimal passage

Name: dacryocystocele
Definition: An acute inflammation of lacrimal passage that is characterized by inflammation of the lacrimal sac

Name: obsolete Congenital or acquired abnormality of vulva complicating pregnancy
Definition: An acute inflammation of lacrimal passage that is characterized by inflammation of the lacrimal sac
